    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128030/extras/21e7ee2d81fa59f1f5de2319710b8227.avif?t=1663009299\" width=600 height=83 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于游戏</h2>这是一款3D平台控制的游戏. 游戏玩法是用手把上的四个按键来控制太空碟，并飞往动物上方吸走它们来完成不同关卡。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏背景</h2>你有一个任务就是要捉走动物园的动物，所以一个昏昏欲睡的想法溜进你的脑海，后来发现所有的动物都在路上逃走了。而你正在控制一个看起来像宇宙飞船的东西。你看到了你的绿色手臂，这根本不像人类！快去抓动物吧！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >控制方法</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128030/extras/cbba690f64540836b52161e8e6a8928d.poster.avif?t=1663009299\" width=600 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128030/extras/cbba690f64540836b52161e8e6a8928d.webm?t=1663009299\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128030/extras/cbba690f64540836b52161e8e6a8928d.mp4?t=1663009299\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>左前键 - LT / 右前键 - RT<br></li><li>左后键 - LB / 右后键 - RB</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128030/extras/0e79f4f6173da2a38a4e009142f3ec25.poster.avif?t=1663009299\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128030/extras/0e79f4f6173da2a38a4e009142f3ec25.webm?t=1663009299\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128030/extras/0e79f4f6173da2a38a4e009142f3ec25.mp4?t=1663009299\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128030/extras/9af9a372abf5ac069fdc07769b5c8ac2.poster.avif?t=1663009299\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128030/extras/9af9a372abf5ac069fdc07769b5c8ac2.webm?t=1663009299\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128030/extras/9af9a372abf5ac069fdc07769b5c8ac2.mp4?t=1663009299\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128030/extras/defa5f2fe0953fce1e43c544764c07a6.poster.avif?t=1663009299\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128030/extras/defa5f2fe0953fce1e43c544764c07a6.webm?t=1663009299\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128030/extras/defa5f2fe0953fce1e43c544764c07a6.mp4?t=1663009299\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128030/extras/c45c82d5742803c139ec251bb58e28f9.poster.avif?t=1663009299\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128030/extras/c45c82d5742803c139ec251bb58e28f9.webm?t=1663009299\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128030/extras/c45c82d5742803c139ec251bb58e28f9.mp4?t=1663009299\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>20个关卡(超级简单！)<br></li><li>心灵扭曲的控制<br></li><li>我不认为你可以一分钟内完成第一关<br></li><li>这是一款简单的游戏<br></li><li>不要打烂你的手把<br></li><li>没有事情是不可能的</li></ul>",
